column108: Hafsund Feriehytter as / avd Sjøterrassen, Stathelle, Norway, is looking for a chef. Job description We are looking for a motivated and experienced chef to join our team at Sjøterrassen. You will be responsible for preparing and cooking our à la carte dishes to a high standard, ensuring that the kitchen is clean and organized, and working closely with the head chef and the rest of the team to provide our guests with an unforgettable dining experience. We are looking for someone with a passion for cooking, strong skills under pressure, and the ability to thrive in a fast-paced environment. Skills Quality Control Communication ++ Hygiene and Safety Stress Management Customer Service and Guest Satisfaction Language: speak English or scandinavian must. Working hours 40 hours week at Hafsundveien 10, 3967 Stathelle, Norway Period Start of June to end of august 2025 Salary NOK 235/hour Other information	 Some of the staff will stay in a shared cabin, only five minutes' walk from the restaurant. The cabins are well-equipped with all necessary facilities for a practical and comfortable living experience. More information Tommy Larsen, +47 9408 6351, Post@sjoterrassen.com How to apply? Send your application to Tommy Larsen at Post@sjoterrassen.com Latest application date is 01.03.2025 (from NAV EURES Norway) Sjøterrassen is more than just a restaurant – it’s a place where the beauty of nature meets lively activities and great food. Located along the coast, just a short drive from the nearest city, Sjøterrassen is a popular destination for both locals and visitors. Here, guests can enjoy concerts, motorshows, and exciting events while relaxing on our beach or exploring our guest harbor. For our employees, we focus on creating a positive and energetic work environment where well-being is a top priority. We believe that a good team that thrives together produces the best results, which is why we place great emphasis on creating a workplace where everyone feels seen and valued.  Working at Sjøterrassen gives you the opportunity to be part of creating unforgettable experiences for both guests and colleagues in an inspiring seaside setting. http://www.sjoterrassen.no/
